    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People or corporate bodies in the construction industry that undertake work as detailed in a legally binding contractual agreement, and whose services are limited to the construction of commercial buildings and single-dwelling or multiple-dwelling residential buildings. For contractors on a construction project whose services are unlimited, use "general contractors."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
